From 44a8d32576afbd14d4c3e65d498e1cd63190ceae Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Andrew Udvare <audvare@gmail.com>
Date: Sun, 8 Feb 2026 20:56:18 -0500
Subject: [PATCH 19/23] Add USE_SYSTEM_IMGUI option for system imgui

- third_party/CMakeLists.txt: link system imgui (pkg-config) when
  USE_SYSTEM_IMGUI is set, else build the bundled copy.
- src/xenia/base/imgui_include.h and imgui_internal_include.h: new wrappers
  selecting <imgui/imgui.h> / <imgui/imgui_internal.h> when XENIA_USE_SYSTEM_IMGUI
  is defined.
- Route imgui includes throughout src through the wrappers.

Co-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>
---
